             - Version 1.1
==========================
* Made HTTP headers available to the endpoint.
* Added handling of OPTIONS method to support CORS requests.
* Added CSRF protection mechanism. 
* Changed the behaviour of 'Access-Control-Allow-Origin' response header: it 
  will be added with a value of '*' only if not set by the endpoint.   
* Added /Health endpoint for load balancer checks.
* Improved handling of cases where the client closes the connection before
  we begin to send our answer.
* Fixed a case in QuotedPrintable decoder which may lead to incorrect decoding.
* Added unit tests. 

June 4, 2014 - Version 1.0
==========================
* Initial release.
